    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamental containers of various designs, usually relatively squat, for holding or growing plants or flowers. For containers that are not particularly ornamental, use "flowerpots." For ornamental containers for holding or concealing a flowerpot, use "cachepots." .For vase-shaped containers for cut flowers, use "flower vases."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046683/Random House Dictionary of the English Language (1966)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093897/Metropolitan Museum of Art [online] (2001-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Recipientes ornamentales para colocar o cultivar plantas o flores. Use "cache-pot" para recipientes ornamentales usados para contener u ocultar una maceta.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sierhouders voor het houden of kweken van planten of bloemen. Gebruik 'cachepots' voor sierhouders om een bloempot in te zetten of aan het oog te onttrekken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
